Package: CEClust
Type: Package
Title: Compact Composite Entropy Clustering Grid Explorer
Version: 0.2.0.9001
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Thierry",
      family = "Dumont",
      email = "tdumont@parisnanterre.fr",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Author: Thierry Dumont [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Thierry Dumont <tdumont@parisnanterre.fr>
Description: Fits composite entropy clustering grids with a compact result
    format focused on the final phase diagram, selected partitions, stability
    diagnostics, saturation diagnostics, sensitivity summaries, and the Shiny
    explorer. Dense per-task matrices are discarded as soon as they are no
    longer needed, which keeps large C by lambda runs manageable.
